---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | Maple Tyne Technologies" description="Terms of Service for Maple-Tyne Technologies Inc., headquartered in Toronto, Ontario.">
	<main class="page-container">
    <section class="page-header">
      <h1 class="gradient-text">Terms of Service</h1>
    </section>

		<div class="content-section">
      <p>Welcome to Maple-Tyne Technologies Inc., headquartered in Toronto, Ontario.</p>

      <p>By accessing our website, ventures, or engineering platforms, you agree to our terms. Our products, including our Energy Management System and micro-SaaS utilities like the Invoice Generator, are provided to facilitate structural, intelligent automation and high-utility orchestration.</p>

      <p>While our automated systems are designed to maximize financial returns—such as yielding estimated utility reductions based on regional grid metrics and tariff structures—actual savings may vary depending on individual driving routines and home baselines.</p>

      <p>All intellectual property and localized architectural models remain the exclusive property of Maple-Tyne Technologies Inc.</p>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-container {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .content-section p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>
